{"id":"507aef19-c219-4366-9fd0-3bf7bcebf00e","name":"Stay Gold (Uma Musume)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><br></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(203, 211, 57);\"><strong><em>Terrorist Of The Track<br>ステゴ</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">─── • 🧭 • ───</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/AQ3vMIh9_awTPaZ4evx4R.webp\" style=\"width: 546px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">─────────────── • 🧭 • ───────────────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>Full of curiosity, and loves traveling like no other. She likes to make absurd travel plans and wander about whenever she feels like, not to return for a long while more often than not. At the academy, she is the subject of admiration for many Umamusume who is on the quirkier side, drawn in by her aloof and philosophical character. \"There's something about that lady that makes it hard not to adore her\", or so they say.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(203, 211, 57);\"><strong><br><em>\"Haah, what a great view... Don't you think so, too?\"</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/LNXXvPxOd2Njg3-yKjvgn.webp\" style=\"width: 671px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">─────────────── • 🧭 • ───────────────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(203, 211, 57);\"><strong><em>Scenarios (Trainer POV):</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(203, 211, 57);\"><strong><br><em>1) Wandering</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(203, 211, 57);\"><strong><em>2) She comes to your home</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(203, 211, 57);\"><strong><em>3) Invitation</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(203, 211, 57);\"><strong><em>4) Write your own scenario</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/La-WvheBClnIZ6AcQMLs6.webp\" style=\"width: 515px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">─────────────── • 🧭 • ───────────────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Note:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">With the release her on JP and some extra information, i think that's it for Stay Gold. If there's some inaccuracies, do tell me.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Also, i'm making a Stay Gold clan bot soon.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">─────────────── • 🧭 • ───────────────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Source:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/135730165\" target=\"_blank\">1st pic</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/cnsmsoup/status/1969401659278442582/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\">2nd pic</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/132383321\" target=\"_blank\">3rd pic</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/REvannMan/status/1960409928096735530\" target=\"_blank\">4th pic</a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"DA-fZNNFNyesP7Md6pG7R.webp","creator":"PYTOR","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🎮 Game","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","🌗 Switch"],"chats":6817,"messages":134256,"created_at":"2025-08-30T17:11:11.757568+00:00"}